name: DJI 2212 920KV Brushless Motor
description:
2212 920KV CW CCW self-locking Bruhsless Motor For DJI Phantom F330 F450 F550 4 axis 6 axis RC Muticopter Quadcopter FPV Drone

All motors have been dynamically balanced. Excellent performance

Suitable for DJI Phantom series Drone/Universal 450-550mm 4 axis 6 axis RC Muticopter

Model: 2212 Brushless Motor
KV value: KV 920
Motor size: 28mm*24mm
Stator size: 22mm*12mm
Direction: CW forward (black) CCW reverse (silver)
Support lithium battery: 3S-4S LIPO

Adaptable blades: DJI series recommends 9443 carbon fiber propellers, three-blade propellers, two-blade propellers and white self-locking propellers. F450 and F550 are recommended for use with 9443 propellers

name: DJI FPV Remote Controller
description: The DJI Digital FPV System was designed for the drone racing industry. It consists of the DJI FPV Air Unit Module, DJI FPV Camera, DJI FPV Goggles, and DJI FPV Remote Controller, all of which are packed with powerful features and serve a significant role in the development of our HD Low Latency FPV system.
